videos.desc: Just this year I’m going to 10 weddings, so I cooked up this new series: Table for 2. While this is great for couples, it works perfectly for hosting one other person, if you want dinner and next day’s lunch and of course you can scale this up for more servings. Episode 1 is Chipotle Honey Salmon Bowls from @halfbakedharvest . It’s so easy and the salad, rice, and sauces are ready by the time your salmon is done. You can find all your ingredients at TJs! Hope you enjoy! #traderjoes
videos.author: joes.before.bros
